  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca - \u0db4\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0d9f\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Diesel-Petrol shortage again",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ceylon Petroleum Private Tanker Owners' Association Joint Secretary D. said that the petroleum corporation is not getting stocks of both types of fuel, diesel and petrol, and due to this there has been a shortage of fuel all over the country. V. Mr. Shanta Silva said today (25).",
        "Mr. Shanta Silva said that many petrol stations have been closed due to the lack of fuel and due to these conditions quite long queues have formed again near the petrol stations."
      ],
